    <p>
      Before you start searching for a job, it’s important to network with 
      people in your industry, develop confidence in your interview skills, 
      and create a strong resume and cover letter. <span class="full-blurb">In order to stand out 
      among a sea of applicants, having a strong resume and cover letter are 
      imperative. These documents should specifically cater to the position 
      in which you are applying while also highlighting your skills and 
      experiences. The Career Center offers many resources to help in the 
